## Why This Matters

If context is not validated before entry:

- invalid input → becomes state  
- state → becomes memory  
- memory → shapes decisions  

---

## AATP Assertions

- Traceability ≠ Validity  
- Memory ≠ Authority  
- Execution ≠ Control  

